Sample-Level Metadata for the Exposome Challenge Dataset

Source: R/data_meta.R
meta.Rd

A data.frame of maternal-child metadata including sample identifiers, demographic information, clinical outcomes and exposure information.

Usage

meta

Format

A data.frame with one row per sample and columns including:

hs_child_age_None

Child age in years.

e3_sex_None

Biological sex (Male/Female).

h_cohort

Cohort identifier.

hs_asthma

Binary indicator of asthma outcome.

...

Additional exposure and phenotype variables.

Source

Derived from the ISGlobal Exposome Data Challenge 2021.

Examples

data(meta)
